item.title: CVE-2024-25962|2024-03-27T10:37:43.037Z -- Dell -- InsightIQ
item.description: Dell InsightIQ, version 5.0, contains an improper access control vulnerability. A remote low privileged attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to unauthorized access to monitoring data.
